title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Leber/Robson/Talkers
description: Show kicks off with Wild coach Bruce Boudreau ahead of tonight's tilt in Jersey, then celebrates the US women striking gold in Olympic hockey. Leber in studio middle hour, Britt Robson with Wolves analysis final hour, and more!
